#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Some Fundamentals"
msgstr "Neke osnove"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:4
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kwrite; is very simple to use. Anyone that has used a text editor should "
#| "have no problems."
msgid ""
"&kwrite; and many other &katepart; users are very simple to use. Anyone that "
"has used a text editor should have no problems."
msgstr ""
"<application>K‑pisanje</application> se vrlo jednostavno koristi. Ko god je "
"već koristio neki uređivač teksta, neće imati nikakvih problema."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag and Drop"
msgstr "Prevlačenje"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:12
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kwrite; uses the &kde; Drag and Drop protocol. Files may be dragged and "
#| "dropped onto &kwrite; from the Desktop, the filemanager &dolphin;, or "
#| "some remote &FTP; site opened in one of &dolphin;'s windows."
msgid ""
"&katepart; uses the &kde; Drag and Drop protocol. Files may be dragged and "
"dropped onto &katepart; from the Desktop, the filemanager &dolphin;, or some "
"remote &FTP; site opened in one of &dolphin;'s windows."
msgstr ""
"<application>K‑pisanje</application> koristi <acronym>KDE‑ov</acronym> "
"protokol prevlačenja. Fajlovi se mogu prevlačiti na <application>K‑pisanje</"
"application> sa površi, iz menadžera fajlova <application>Dolphina</"
"application>, ili udaljenog FTP sajta otvorenog u jednom od "
"<application>Dolphinovih</application> prozora."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcuts"
msgstr "Prečice"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:22
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Many of the shortcuts are configurable by way of the <link linkend="
#| "\"settings\">Settings</link> menu. By default &kwrite; honors the "
